1958;;Voice in the Mirror;;American;;Harry Keller;;Richard Egan, Julie London, Walter Matthau;;film noir;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Voice_in_the_Mirror;;After sinking into the depths of drunken despair due to the death of his daughter, a man is warned by his doctor that he is on the brink of terminal mental illness. Struck by a fellow alcoholic's suggestion that perhaps he should try faith, he begins saving not only himself but others, eventually creating Alcoholics Anonymous.